set="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-lgbt-grammy-nominations-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>反思了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">2024 年格莱美</a>提名中 LGBTQ+ 的积极表现。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/boygenius-the-record-review-the-instant-classic-we-were-hoping-for-3419059">Boygenius – 《The Record》评论：我们期待的即时经典</a></strong></li></ul><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">Julien Baker</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">Lucy Dacus</a>组成的超级组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-grammys-2024-nominations-3536101">上周获得了 2024 年格莱美奖的六项提名</a>，其中包括《The Record》和《Not Strong Enough》分别获得年度专辑奖和年度唱片奖。</p><p> Bridgers 还凭借与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>合作的《Ghost In The Machine》第七次获得最佳流行二重奏/团体表演提名。</p><p>在最近接受<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/culture/pride/boygenius-react-2024-grammy-nominations-1235468447/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em>采访时，Boygenius 回顾了他们的提名，并分享了他们对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-monet">维多利亚·莫奈</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>和布兰迪·克拉克等所有提名者中更广泛的 LGBTQ+ 代表性的看法。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzeS8rXgDzZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;u